Package io.github.shuoros.jcompressor.compress

Class ZipCompressor

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.shuoros.jcompressor.compress.ZipCompressor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JCompressor
    public class ZipCompressor
extends Object
implements JCompressor
    This class is an implementation of the JCompressor class and specially implements methods for compressing and extracting zip files.

      • compress

        public void compress()
        Compresses the inner file of instance in same directory and same name(+.zip). If you construct your instance with no inner file in it this method will throw a NoFileToCompressException.

      • compress

        public void compress​(File destinationFile)
        Compresses the inner file of instance in your given destination. If you construct your instance with no inner file in it this method will throw a NoFileToCompressException.
        Parameters:
        destinationFile - Destination where you want your compressed file to be saved.
